arch-info
---------

This program gives some info on the architecture.

Compile and run:

    cc -o arch-info arch-info.c
    ./arch-info

Result (on an x86-64 CPU):

    Endianness:
    -----------
    This processor is using little-endian order.
    The integer 0x1234abcd is stored as [cd ab 34 12] in memory.

    Data type sizes:
    ----------------
          pointer   8 bytes
             char   1 bytes
        short int   2 bytes
              int   4 bytes
         long int   8 bytes
    long long int   8 bytes
            float   4 bytes
           double   8 bytes
      long double  16 bytes
